<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">I haven't really spent time doing trade skills (too many fun quests out there!)
<br />
So, I've read with interest about the fun people are having doing the trade skills.. Can someone either point me to a basic primer to get involved with these or briefly explain the process to me?
<br />
I know I skill up my harvesting type skills by carrying out the various functions around the land (mining, gathering etc.) I also understand that I need to go to the tradeskill areas to work my skills up. I've only really done this last step on the Isle of Refuge. As I am in Freeport, what should my next steps be? I assume I should continue working my harvesting skills but the rest is a little foggy to me. Are there places to practice my skills? I understand that I need to join some groups but I don't know about them. Also, I understand I can get quests from these groups to help them advance. My standing with these groups improves and I can get better quests etc. So, if you feel like answering these questions, please do so. I am sure he answers are already all over some sites (possibly this one) but I've not been able to find them..
<br />

<br />
Thank you in advance.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
